            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae Aventiae <lb n="2"/>et <expan><abbr>Gen</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>incolar</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Ianuarius <lb n="4"/>Florinus <lb n="5"/>et <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Domitius <lb n="6"/>Didymus <lb n="7"/>curatores <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>ex stipe annua <lb n="9"/>adiectis de suo <lb n="10"/>|(sestertiis) <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ummum</ex></expan> |(milia) D
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Basis, Bekrönung und Sockel abgearbeitet. (B): Walser: Z. 7: col(onarum).</p>
            </div>
